 ZooKeeper 3.5 has a transitive dependency on a zookeeper-jute artifact.
 ./distro/src/main/assembly/plugin-trino.xml should have
"<include>org.apache.zookeeper:zookeeper-jute:jar:${zookeeper.version}</include>"

